abstract: "A Claude Code plugin for maintaining project rhythm across sessions,
  context switches, and parallel agents — using a small set of living docs
  (HANDOFF.md, SESSION_LOG.md, LESSONS.md, DECISIONS.md, GOTCHAS.md,
  BACKLOG.md) and the skills + slash commands that maintain them."
